            "title": "Fact-Check - Meta Fights For Money, Not Speech",
            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404146717/image_1404146717.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Facebook\" data-id=\"1404146717\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404146717/image_1404146717.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404146717/image_1404146717.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404146717/image_1404146717.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404146717/image_1404146717.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404146717/image_1404146717.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404146717/image_1404146717.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404146717/image_1404146717.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404146717/image_1404146717.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">panida wijitpanya</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Breakingviews</em></p> <p>Mark Zuckerberg is more interested in the bottom line than the First Amendment. The Meta Platforms (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/META\" title=\"Meta Platforms, Inc.\">META</a>) boss touted “free expression” as the motivating factor for reversing the company’s policy about moderating posts on Facebook and</p>",
